{"id": 225039456, "title": "Colorado weather: Scattered thunderstorms expected Wednesday afternoon", "text": "Scattered thunderstorms are expected across Colorado this afternoon, bringing the potential for hail \u2014 especially in the Eastern Plains, according to the National Weather Service in Boulder. Storms are likely to develop in the Urban Corridor between 3 p.m. and 7 p.m., while those in the Eastern Plains are likely to arrive between 4 p.m. and 10 p.m., according to the weather service. The storms could become severe and bring golf ball size hail and heavy winds. The largest threat of severe weather will be east of Fort Morgan and Limon, according to the weather service.", "summary": "Scattered thunderstorms are expected across Colorado this afternoon, bringing the potential for hail -- especially in the Eastern Plains, according to the National Weather Service in Boulder.\u00a0", "url": "https://www.denverpost.com/2024/05/29/colorado-weather-rain-thunderstorms-hail-wednesday-afternoon/", "image": "https://www.denverpost.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TDP-L-FRONT-RANGE-WEATHER_DSC5767.jpg?w=1024", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-05-29 12:42:45", "author": "Jessica Seaman", "authors": ["Jessica Seaman"], "language": "en", "source_country": "US", "sentiment": -0.093}